## A Paradigm Shift

In [a href:"https://www.wired.com/2014/08/shark-cable/" target:"_blank"]2014[/a], Google had to shark-proof their underwater cables.
It turned out that sharks were fond of chewing on the high-speed cables that make up the internet.
While this is not an issue anymore, it's a reminder that both the internet and sharks share the same home.

[LargeAside]
